    public interface THasPropertyChange
    This interface implements a wrapper based on the java.beans.PropertyChangeSupport class so that all TEAL objects will be able to access an internal PropertyChangeSupport member as if they were derived from one if. It does not seem that Java supplies a standard interface or base class for beans.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.9 $
    Author:
    Andrew McKinney, Phil Bailey, Michael Danziger
